{"tid":1788141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"演算法牽制YouTuber 為爭訂閱壓力大","createTime":"2019-12-18T12:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T12:16:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d90ce541a72bafc822e7f093d7f1058db075c3c8","tid":1788141,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191217/QGUXOYDLZYYWBQI67DXUISW6JM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191217%2FQGUXOYDLZYYWBQI67DXUISW6JM%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6nqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=727e0aca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191217%2FQGUXOYDLZYYWBQI67DXUISW6JM%2F&h=49efc05f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191217/QGUXOYDLZYYWBQI67DXUISW6JM/</a><br />\n<br />\n演算法牽制YouTuber 為爭訂閱壓力大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191217/large/1576512306_0ac4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576512306_0ac4.gif&h=090390d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿格達姆曾因收視下跌血洗YouTube總部。<br />\n<br />\n超級網紅PewDiePie非首次言休，三年前曾揚言沒靈感想退出，約一周後又重返YouTube。其他全職YouTuber深明這欲斷難斷的予盾，既愛頻道帶來的名利愛戴，但又恨被演算法（algorithm）牽着走；長期度橋拍片及討好粉絲會造成倦怠，無情留言和恐嚇甚至引致創傷後遺，逾百萬訂閱的ShoddyCast頻道主胡里根開玩笑說：「YouTube應贊助大家看心理醫生。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n失收視闖YouTube總部開槍<br />\n<br />\n演算法是YouTube編碼系統，猜測網民興趣再推介短片，廣告商亦按演算法決定在哪個頻道落廣告。演算法不時因各種因素改變，YouTuber只能靠訂閱數作唯一依據。胡里根說為保收入穩定，一邊密密拍片吸引粉絲訂閱追看，一邊擔心被後浪取代，造成精神壓力，若以個人生活為主題拍片，公私不分令精神更難放鬆。最極端例子是38歲女YouTuber阿格達姆，因歸咎演算法和審查令她失去收視，去年4月闖入YouTube加州總部槍傷3人再吞槍自殺。<br />\n<br />\n加州大學歐文分校研究員Katherine Lo說在創作和剪接以外，頻道主還要應付許多「無形而疲累的勞動」，例如在社交網保持活躍、看留言與粉絲互動、接洽贊助捐款、保持聲譽和同業關係。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》"},{"pid":"22bfeb9e3f0ecdc51719a93122a34ba3de8eee08","tid":1788141,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e390c35c0b77106944f9068f1b1fc4bd4ee02348","tid":1788141,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2509391e2dad430dbdeacea4a78a54787f9d851","tid":1788141,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14d23224211c3f8dbc166bbf09f0a59987409ea7","tid":1788141,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"難怪B先生咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b62eff0c422252715f7503c0dd235ca4995eb9f","tid":1788141,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}